{"tid":1829571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］中國武漢急增17宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案","createTime":"2020-01-18T23:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T02:30:06.000Z","uid":91914,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8032b9c767e4cba50441b78c1f5e19e0480a0319","tid":1829571,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T23:48:33.000Z","msg":"中國武漢市衛健委今晨突然公佈，當地新增17宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案，其中3宗屬於嚴重，累積個案為62宗。<br />\n通報稱，上星期五（十五）確診17宗新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎病例，分別是12男、5女，年齡介乎30至79歲，都在本月十三日前發病，正追蹤他們的密切接觸者。除2人病情危重暫不適宜轉院外，其餘15名患者已轉送金銀潭醫院集中治療。<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/01/19/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%AA%81%E5%A2%9E17%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8B%80%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F19%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%25A2%259E17%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%259C%2589%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1G9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=85f946c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/01/19/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%AA%81%E5%A2%9E17%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8B%80%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89/</a>"},{"pid":"c5d5b3f5cd3e5624bd900fbe68ed8f8c95c9cc5b","tid":1829571,"uid":91914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T23:49:27.000Z","msg":"陣間一定要個個帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3a5302e027c0815126c5323306e4fa3f94d3ce","tid":1829571,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T23:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s